<plot>This short focuses on the job of the costume designer in the production of motion pictures. The costume designer must design clothing that is correct for the film historically and geographically, and must be appropriate for the mood of the individual scene. We see famed costume designer 'Edith Head' (qv) at work on a production.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?550346</url></doc>
